messages.TRMSG_PRE_BATTLE:
Look, look! Look at my Pokémon!
It’s really cool!
messages.TRMSG_DEFEAT:
Wowee! I had to hold on tight to
my inflatable tube!
messages.TRMSG_POST_BATTLE:
Pools are OK, but I like the sea
because Pokémon live there.
messages.TRMSG_REMATCH:
Yay! You came to see my Pokémon
again, right? Look, look!
